body:
Hey Rito Board,

So my friend has been having this issue with bugsplats nearly every game. He'd bug splat, but then he'd be able to play the game through but would have to restart once the match was over.  Deciding to reinstall, he's now been hit with an issue of just not being able to do it. Usually he gets to 30-40% before bugsplating and then it restarts at a lower percentage. 

We've been trying various 'fixes' and ways to install the game all day but still no dice when it comes to getting it to work.  Any suggestions about approaching this?

