replies.body:
Rito Board here!  It's hard to say why your friend is bugsplatting, but I appreciate you reaching out for him.  Sometimes this can be caused by bad drives, bad game files, or a hardware issue.  Have him go through our [game crash](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201761974-Bug-Splat-and-Game-Crashes+) guide to rule out any possibilities and get it fixed up.  I hope that helps!  

Rito Board out!
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}

Hey there Porocles and thank you for getting back to this! 

From what he's told me, he's already seen that and been through the entire thing but still no dice when it comes to  installing. After he uninstalled yesterday, we had him go through it and tried other things that people on the boards/reddit have said and still nothing. Still gets stuck at 30-42% bugsplats and then gets knocked back to 30 or lower.

